- YOU'RE NOT IN TROUBLE AT ALL,
I WAS JOKING.

00:05:32.199 --> 00:05:34.301
- SO REALLY?
IT DOES WORK OUT?

00:05:34.301 --> 00:05:35.502
- YEAH, IT'S NOT ILLEGAL.

00:05:35.502 --> 00:05:36.904
- OKAY.
- I MEAN, HE'S NOT A REAL COP,

00:05:36.904 --> 00:05:38.405
HE'S A STRIPPER, YEAH.
- THAT'S OKAY.

00:05:38.405 --> 00:05:40.440
BUT TO BRING
A STRIPPER TO A BUSINESSMAN,

00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:42.075
IT'S NOT A REALLY
GOOD IDEA, NO.

00:05:42.075 --> 00:05:43.243
- OH, YOU DON'T LIKE IT?

00:05:43.243 --> 00:05:44.411
[music stops]
- NOT AT ALL. LIKE, OKAY--

00:05:44.411 --> 00:05:45.512
- WELL, IT WAS A JOKE,
YOU KNOW,

00:05:45.512 --> 00:05:47.147
LIKE, YOU THOUGHT HE WAS A COP.
YOU KNOW?

00:05:47.147 --> 00:05:48.649
- THAT'S WHAT I'M SAYING,
EVEN IF IT'S GONNA BE A JOKE,

00:05:48.649 --> 00:05:51.785
NATHAN, TO BRING A BUSINESSMAN,
BRING HIM, LIKE, STRIPPER--

00:05:51.785 --> 00:05:55.222
A GUY STRIPPER, IT'S NOT REALLY
GONNA BE THE COOL THING TO HAVE.

00:05:55.222 --> 00:05:57.558
- ALL RIGHT.

